original_title: Umphrey's McGee: Live At Stubbs BBQ 4/20/2013
overview: Umphrey’s rolled into Austin, Texas ready to rage at what has been their 4/20 destination spot for three years running: the famous Stubb’s Waller Creek Amphitheatre. Spirits were high as fans swarmed Red River and started flowing into the venue for the highly anticipated sold out show.
title: Umphrey's McGee: Live At Stubbs BBQ 4/20/2013
